            Yet out of that Graue in one true and most Orthodoxe sense are we brought, not by getting out, if we euer had been actually in, but because that wee know he is the Lord, whose mercifull preuention hath bar'd vp the euerlasting doores of that Graue to vs that are out: and to that purpose hee sent the Angell in the Reuelation from Heauen, hauing the Key of the bottomelesse Pit,
